notes:
This dataset contains human casualties due to major disater such as flood and landslides, Earthquake, Windstorms, halitstrosm and thuderbolt, Avalanche, Fire, Cold wave, Drowning and Stampede for 1983 to 2013. The data sets is extracted from Environmental Statistics, 2013.
